This is Volonic Valet 3 from @wearevolonic 

Premium quality wireless charger with Aluminum and Alcantara build, 18 coil matrix featuring Aira’s FreePower tech which brings full surface and position-free wireless charging, up to 3 Qi-enabled devices simultaneously 🙌

You can customize your Volonic with different materials like matte / glossy Aluminum, Alcantara or Leather, and different colors like black, white, silver, red, blue, green, orange and more 👌

I really liked the unboxing experience as well as using it 👍 Works perfectly, charges my iPhone, Android devices and AirPods

node.text:
Hey! Here’s my unboxing and first look at the new POCO X3 Pro in Frost Blue color! 🔥

It looks really cool and have amazing specs for its price: 6.67” 120Hz display, Snapdragon 860, 48MP Quad camera, 5160mAh battery with 33W fast changing and stereo speakers! All this for just $199 👏

I think this is just an amazing deal for what you are getting, I had this phone for a week and I like it! If you have any questions about this phone, let me know in the comments below! 👀

#Xiaomi #POCO #POCOX3Pro

node.title: POCO X3 Pro - Unboxing & First Look! 🔥
